1) Bazylak forces you to go to lecture by making attendance mandatory through in class Quercus questions. 2) The course is poorly organized, and had an excessive amount of assignments and projects. 3) In two occasions in which I needed assistance with the course, I tried to get assistance from Bazylak, but he was not only unhelpful but rude too.
very encouraging and helpful professor when you need help. nicest guy during office hours and for capstone projects. he's there for almost every event. and always happy and smiling.
